{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"This technology"},{"time":3000,"text":"made a very important impact on us."},{"time":5000,"text":"It changed the way our history developed."},{"time":9000,"text":"But it's a technology so pervasive,"},{"time":11000,"text":"so invisible,"},{"time":13000,"text":"that we, for a long time,"},{"time":15000,"text":"forgot to take it into account"},{"time":18000,"text":"when we talked about"},{"time":20000,"text":"human evolution."},{"time":22000,"text":"But we see the results of this technology, still."},{"time":25000,"text":"So let's make a little test."},{"time":27000,"text":"So everyone of you turns to their neighbor please."},{"time":31000,"text":"Turn and face your neighbors."},{"time":33000,"text":"Please, also on the balcony."},{"time":36000,"text":"Smile. Smile. Open the mouths."},{"time":38000,"text":"Smile, friendly."},{"time":40000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":42000,"text":"Do you --"},{"time":44000,"text":"Do you see any Canine teeth?"},{"time":47000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":49000,"text":"Count Dracula teeth"},{"time":52000,"text":"in the mouths of your neighbors?"},{"time":54000,"text":"Of course not."},{"time":56000,"text":"Because our dental anatomy"},{"time":59000,"text":"is actually made,"},{"time":61000,"text":"not for tearing down raw meat from bones"},{"time":64000,"text":"or chewing fibrous leaves for hours."},{"time":69000,"text":"It is made for a diet"},{"time":71000,"text":"which is soft, mushy,"},{"time":74000,"text":"which is reduced in fibers,"},{"time":77000,"text":"which is very easily chewable"},{"time":79000,"text":"and digestible."},{"time":82000,"text":"Sounds like fast food, doesn't it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":86000,"text":"It's for cooked food."},{"time":89000,"text":"We carry in our face the proof"},{"time":92000,"text":"that cooking,"},{"time":94000,"text":"food transformation,"},{"time":97000,"text":"made us what we are."},{"time":99000,"text":"So I would suggest that we change how we classify ourselves."},{"time":102000,"text":"We talk about ourselves as omnivores."},{"time":105000,"text":"I would say, we should call ourselves coctivors --"},{"time":108000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":110000,"text":"from coquere, to cook."},{"time":113000,"text":"We are the animals"},{"time":115000,"text":"who eat cooked food."},{"time":118000,"text":"No, no, no, no. Better --"},{"time":120000,"text":"to live of cooked food."},{"time":122000,"text":"So cooking is a very important technology."},{"time":124000,"text":"It's technology."},{"time":126000,"text":"I don't know how you feel,"},{"time":128000,"text":"but I like to cook for entertainment."},{"time":130000,"text":"And you need some design"},{"time":132000,"text":"to be successful."},{"time":134000,"text":"So, cooking is a very important technology,"},{"time":137000,"text":"because it allowed us to acquire"},{"time":140000,"text":"what brought you all here:"},{"time":143000,"text":"the big brain,"},{"time":145000,"text":"this wonderful cerebral cortex we have."},{"time":148000,"text":"Because brains are expensive."},{"time":151000,"text":"Those have to pay tuition fees know."},{"time":154000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":156000,"text":"But it's also, metabolically speaking, expensive."},{"time":160000,"text":"You now, our brain is two to three percent of the body mass,"},{"time":163000,"text":"but actually it uses 25 percent of the total energy we use."},{"time":166000,"text":"It's very expensive."},{"time":168000,"text":"Where does the energy come from. Of course, from food."},{"time":171000,"text":"If we eat raw food,"},{"time":173000,"text":"we cannot release really the energy."},{"time":177000,"text":"So this ingenuity of our ancestors,"},{"time":180000,"text":"to invent this most marvelous technology."},{"time":183000,"text":"Invisible -- everyone of us does it every day, so to speak."},{"time":187000,"text":"Cooking made it possible"},{"time":189000,"text":"that mutations,"},{"time":191000,"text":"natural selections, our environment,"},{"time":193000,"text":"could develop us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":197000,"text":"So if we think about"},{"time":199000,"text":"this unleashing human potential,"},{"time":202000,"text":"which was possible by cooking and food,"},{"time":205000,"text":"why do we talk so badly about food?"},{"time":208000,"text":"Why is it always do and don'ts"},{"time":210000,"text":"and it's good for you, it's not good for you?"},{"time":212000,"text":"I think the good news for me"},{"time":214000,"text":"would be if we could go back"},{"time":217000,"text":"and talk about the unleashing,"},{"time":219000,"text":"the continuation of the unleashing of human potential."},{"time":222000,"text":"Now, cooking allowed also"},{"time":224000,"text":"that we became a migrant species."},{"time":227000,"text":"We walked out of Africa two times."},{"time":230000,"text":"We populated all the ecologies."},{"time":232000,"text":"If you can cook, nothing can happen to you,"},{"time":235000,"text":"because whatever you find,"},{"time":237000,"text":"you will try to transform it."},{"time":239000,"text":"It keeps also your brain working."},{"time":242000,"text":"Now the very easy and simple technology"},{"time":246000,"text":"which was developed"},{"time":248000,"text":"actually runs after this formula."},{"time":250000,"text":"Take something which looks like food, transform it,"},{"time":253000,"text":"and it gives you a good, very easy, accessible energy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":256000,"text":"This technology affected two organs,"},{"time":259000,"text":"the brain and the gut, which it actually affected."},{"time":262000,"text":"The brain could grow, but the gut actually shrunk."},{"time":265000,"text":"Okay, it's not obvious to be honest."},{"time":267000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":270000,"text":"But it shrunk to 60 percent"},{"time":272000,"text":"of primate gut"},{"time":274000,"text":"of my body mass."},{"time":276000,"text":"So because of having cooked food,"},{"time":279000,"text":"it's easier to digest."},{"time":282000,"text":"Now having a large brain, as you know,"},{"time":285000,"text":"is a big advantage,"},{"time":287000,"text":"because you can actually influence your environment."},{"time":290000,"text":"You can influence your own technologies you have invented."},{"time":292000,"text":"You can continue to innovate and invent."},{"time":294000,"text":"Now the big brain did this also with cooking."},{"time":297000,"text":"But how did it actually run this show?"},{"time":300000,"text":"How did it actually interfere?"},{"time":302000,"text":"What kind of criteria did it use?"},{"time":305000,"text":"And this is actually taste reward and energy."},{"time":309000,"text":"You know we have up to five tastes,"},{"time":311000,"text":"three of them sustain us."},{"time":314000,"text":"Sweet -- energy."},{"time":316000,"text":"Umami -- this is a meaty taste."},{"time":318000,"text":"You need proteins for muscles, recovery."},{"time":322000,"text":"Salty,"},{"time":324000,"text":"because you need salt, otherwise your electric body will not work."},{"time":327000,"text":"And two tastes which protect you --"},{"time":330000,"text":"bitter and sour,"},{"time":332000,"text":"which are against"},{"time":335000,"text":"poisonous and rotten material."},{"time":338000,"text":"But of course, they are hard-wired"},{"time":340000,"text":"but we use them still in a sophisticated way."},{"time":342000,"text":"Think about bittersweet chocolate;"},{"time":344000,"text":"or think about the acidity"},{"time":346000,"text":"of yogurt -- wonderful --"},{"time":348000,"text":"mixed with strawberry fruits."}]},{"cues":[{"time":350000,"text":"So we can make mixtures of all this kind of thing"},{"time":353000,"text":"because we know"},{"time":356000,"text":"that, in cooking, we can transform it"},{"time":358000,"text":"to the form."},{"time":360000,"text":"Reward: this is a more complex"},{"time":363000,"text":"and especially integrative"},{"time":366000,"text":"form of our brain"},{"time":368000,"text":"with various different elements --"},{"time":371000,"text":"the external states, our internal states,"},{"time":373000,"text":"how do we feel, and so on are put together."},{"time":376000,"text":"And something which maybe you don't like"},{"time":378000,"text":"but you are so hungry that you really will be satisfied to eat."},{"time":381000,"text":"So satisfaction was a very important part."},{"time":384000,"text":"And as I say, energy was necessary."}]},{"cues":[{"time":386000,"text":"Now how did the gut actually"},{"time":388000,"text":"participate in this development?"},{"time":391000,"text":"And the gut is a silent voice --"},{"time":394000,"text":"it's going more for feelings."},{"time":396000,"text":"I use the euphemism digestive comfort --"},{"time":400000,"text":"actually -- it's a digestive discomfort,"},{"time":403000,"text":"which the gut is concerned with."},{"time":406000,"text":"If you get a stomach ache, if you get a little bit bloated,"},{"time":409000,"text":"was not the right food, was not the right cooking manipulation"},{"time":412000,"text":"or maybe other things went wrong."},{"time":414000,"text":"So my story is a tale of two brains,"},{"time":417000,"text":"because it might surprise you,"},{"time":419000,"text":"our gut has a full-fledged brain."},{"time":422000,"text":"All the managers in the room say,"},{"time":424000,"text":"\"You don't tell me something new, because we know, gut feeling."},{"time":426000,"text":"This is what we are using.\""},{"time":428000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":430000,"text":"And actually you use it and it's actually useful."},{"time":432000,"text":"Because our gut is connected to our emotional limbic system,"},{"time":435000,"text":"they do speak with each other"},{"time":437000,"text":"and make decisions."},{"time":440000,"text":"But what it means"},{"time":442000,"text":"to have a brain there"},{"time":444000,"text":"is that, not only the big brain"},{"time":447000,"text":"has to talk with the food,"},{"time":450000,"text":"the food has to talk with the brain,"},{"time":453000,"text":"because we have to learn actually"},{"time":456000,"text":"how to talk to the brains."}]},{"cues":[{"time":458000,"text":"Now if there's a gut brain,"},{"time":460000,"text":"we should also learn to talk with this brain."},{"time":462000,"text":"Now 150 years ago,"},{"time":464000,"text":"anatomists described very, very carefully --"},{"time":467000,"text":"here is a model of a wall of a gut."},{"time":470000,"text":"I took the three elements --"},{"time":472000,"text":"stomach, small intestine and colon."},{"time":475000,"text":"And within this structure,"},{"time":477000,"text":"you see these two pinkish layers,"},{"time":479000,"text":"which are actually the muscle."},{"time":481000,"text":"And between this muscle, they found nervous tissues,"},{"time":483000,"text":"a lot of nervous tissues,"},{"time":485000,"text":"which penetrate actually the muscle --"},{"time":487000,"text":"penetrate the submucosa,"},{"time":489000,"text":"where you have all the elements for the immune system."},{"time":491000,"text":"The gut is actually the largest immune system,"},{"time":493000,"text":"defending your body."},{"time":495000,"text":"It penetrates the mucosa."},{"time":497000,"text":"This is the layer which actually touches the food you are swallowing"},{"time":500000,"text":"and you digest,"},{"time":502000,"text":"which is actually the lumen."},{"time":504000,"text":"Now if you think about the gut,"},{"time":506000,"text":"the gut is -- if you could stretch it --"},{"time":508000,"text":"40 meters long,"},{"time":510000,"text":"the length of a tennis court."},{"time":512000,"text":"If we could unroll it,"},{"time":514000,"text":"get out all the folds and so on,"},{"time":517000,"text":"it would have 400 sq. meters of surface."}]},{"cues":[{"time":520000,"text":"And now this brain takes care over this,"},{"time":523000,"text":"to move it with the muscles and to do defend the surface"},{"time":526000,"text":"and, of course, digest our food we cook."},{"time":529000,"text":"So if we give you a specification,"},{"time":532000,"text":"this brain, which is autonomous,"},{"time":534000,"text":"have 500 million nerve cells,"},{"time":536000,"text":"100 million neurons --"},{"time":538000,"text":"so around the size of a cat brain,"},{"time":541000,"text":"so there sleeps a little cat --"},{"time":544000,"text":"thinks for itself,"},{"time":546000,"text":"optimizes whatever it digests."},{"time":549000,"text":"It has 20 different neuron types."},{"time":552000,"text":"It's got the same diversity you find actually in a pig brain,"},{"time":554000,"text":"where you have 100 billion neurons."},{"time":557000,"text":"It has autonomous organized microcircuits,"},{"time":560000,"text":"has these programs which run."},{"time":562000,"text":"It senses the food; it knows exactly what to do."},{"time":565000,"text":"It senses it by chemical means"},{"time":567000,"text":"and very importantly by mechanical means,"},{"time":570000,"text":"because it has to move the food --"},{"time":572000,"text":"it has to mix all the various elements"},{"time":574000,"text":"which we need for digestion."},{"time":576000,"text":"This control of muscle is very, very important,"},{"time":579000,"text":"because, you know, there can be reflexes."},{"time":581000,"text":"If you don't like a food, especially if you're a child, you gag."},{"time":584000,"text":"It's this brain which makes this reflex."},{"time":586000,"text":"And then finally,"},{"time":588000,"text":"it controls also the secretion of this molecular machinery,"},{"time":591000,"text":"which actually digests the food we cook."}]},{"cues":[{"time":594000,"text":"Now how do the two brains work with each other?"},{"time":597000,"text":"I took here a model from robotics --"},{"time":600000,"text":"it's called the Subsumption Architecture."},{"time":603000,"text":"What it means is that we have a layered control system."},{"time":606000,"text":"The lower layer, our gut brain,"},{"time":608000,"text":"has its own goals -- digestion defense --"},{"time":611000,"text":"and we have the higher brain"},{"time":613000,"text":"with the goal of integration"},{"time":615000,"text":"and generating behaviors."},{"time":617000,"text":"Now both look -- and this is the blue arrows --"},{"time":620000,"text":"both look to the same food, which is in the lumen"},{"time":623000,"text":"and in the area of your intestine."},{"time":625000,"text":"The big brain integrates signals,"},{"time":627000,"text":"which come from the running programs"},{"time":629000,"text":"of the lower brain,"},{"time":631000,"text":"But subsumption means"},{"time":633000,"text":"that the higher brain can interfere with the lower."},{"time":636000,"text":"It can replace,"},{"time":638000,"text":"or it can inhibit actually, signals."},{"time":641000,"text":"So if we take two types of signals --"},{"time":643000,"text":"a hunger signal for example."},{"time":645000,"text":"If you have an empty stomach,"},{"time":647000,"text":"your stomach produces a hormone called ghrelin."},{"time":649000,"text":"It's a very big signal;"},{"time":651000,"text":"it's sent to the brain says,"},{"time":653000,"text":"\"Go and eat.\""},{"time":655000,"text":"You have stop signals --"},{"time":657000,"text":"we have up to eight stop signals."},{"time":659000,"text":"At least in my case,"},{"time":661000,"text":"they are not listened to."},{"time":663000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":665000,"text":"So what happens"},{"time":667000,"text":"if the big brain in the integration"},{"time":670000,"text":"overrides the signal?"},{"time":672000,"text":"So if you override the hunger signal,"},{"time":674000,"text":"you can have a disorder, which is called anorexia."},{"time":677000,"text":"Despite generating"},{"time":679000,"text":"a healthy hunger signal,"},{"time":681000,"text":"the big brain ignores it"},{"time":683000,"text":"and activates different programs in the gut."},{"time":686000,"text":"The more usual case"},{"time":688000,"text":"is overeating."},{"time":691000,"text":"It actually takes the signal"},{"time":694000,"text":"and changes it,"},{"time":696000,"text":"and we continue,"},{"time":698000,"text":"even [though] our eight signals would say, \"Stop, enough."},{"time":701000,"text":"We have transferred enough energy.\""},{"time":703000,"text":"Now the interesting thing is that,"},{"time":705000,"text":"along this lower layer -- this gut --"},{"time":707000,"text":"the signal becomes stronger and stronger"},{"time":710000,"text":"if undigested, but digestible, material"},{"time":713000,"text":"could penetrate."},{"time":715000,"text":"This we found from bariatric surgery."},{"time":719000,"text":"That then the signal would be very, very high."}]},{"cues":[{"time":722000,"text":"So now back to the cooking question"},{"time":725000,"text":"and back to the design."},{"time":727000,"text":"We have learned to talk to the big brain --"},{"time":730000,"text":"taste and reward, as you know."},{"time":732000,"text":"Now what would be the language"},{"time":734000,"text":"we have to talk to the gut brain"},{"time":736000,"text":"that its signals are so strong"},{"time":738000,"text":"that the big brain cannot ignore it?"},{"time":741000,"text":"Then we would generate something"},{"time":743000,"text":"all of us would like to have --"},{"time":745000,"text":"a balance between the hunger"},{"time":747000,"text":"and the satiation."},{"time":750000,"text":"Now I give you, from our research, a very short claim."},{"time":753000,"text":"This is fat digestion."},{"time":755000,"text":"You have on your left"},{"time":757000,"text":"an olive oil droplet,"},{"time":759000,"text":"and this olive oil droplet gets attacked by enzymes."},{"time":762000,"text":"This is an in vitro experiment."},{"time":764000,"text":"It's very difficult to work in the intestine."},{"time":767000,"text":"Now everyone would expect"},{"time":769000,"text":"that when the degradation of the oil happens,"},{"time":771000,"text":"when the constituents are liberated,"},{"time":773000,"text":"they disappear, they go away"},{"time":775000,"text":"because they [were] absorbed."},{"time":777000,"text":"Actually, what happens is that a very intricate structure appears."},{"time":780000,"text":"And I hope you can see"},{"time":782000,"text":"that there are some ring-like structures in the middle image,"},{"time":784000,"text":"which is water."},{"time":786000,"text":"This whole system generates a huge surface"},{"time":789000,"text":"to allow more enzymes"},{"time":791000,"text":"to attack the remaining oil."},{"time":793000,"text":"And finally, on your right side,"},{"time":795000,"text":"you see a bubbly,"},{"time":797000,"text":"cell-like structure appearing,"},{"time":799000,"text":"from which the body will absorb the fat."},{"time":803000,"text":"Now if we could take this language --"},{"time":805000,"text":"and this is a language of structures --"},{"time":808000,"text":"and make it longer-lasting,"},{"time":811000,"text":"that it can go through"},{"time":813000,"text":"the passage of the intestine,"},{"time":816000,"text":"it would generate stronger signals."}]},{"cues":[{"time":820000,"text":"So our research --"},{"time":822000,"text":"and I think the research also at the universities --"},{"time":824000,"text":"are now fixing on these points"},{"time":826000,"text":"to say: how can we actually --"},{"time":828000,"text":"and this might sound trivial now to you --"},{"time":830000,"text":"how can we change cooking?"},{"time":832000,"text":"How can we cook"},{"time":834000,"text":"that we have this language developed?"},{"time":837000,"text":"So what we have actually, it's not an omnivore's dilemma."},{"time":840000,"text":"We have a coctivor's opportunity,"},{"time":843000,"text":"because we have learned over the last two million years"},{"time":846000,"text":"which taste and reward --"},{"time":849000,"text":"quite sophisticated to cook --"},{"time":851000,"text":"to please ourselves, to satisfy ourselves."},{"time":853000,"text":"If we add the matrix,"},{"time":855000,"text":"if we add the structure language, which we have to learn,"},{"time":858000,"text":"when we learn it, then we can put it back;"},{"time":860000,"text":"and around energy,"},{"time":862000,"text":"we could generate a balance,"},{"time":864000,"text":"which comes out"},{"time":866000,"text":"from our really primordial operation: cooking."},{"time":870000,"text":"So, to make cooking really"},{"time":873000,"text":"a very important element,"},{"time":875000,"text":"I would say even philosophers have to change"},{"time":877000,"text":"and have to finally recognize"},{"time":879000,"text":"that cooking is what made us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":882000,"text":"So I would say, coquo ergo sum:"},{"time":885000,"text":"I cook, therefore I am."},{"time":887000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":889000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}